column2: select top # p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z from photoobj p, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#,#) n where p.objid=n.objid and (p.u BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.g BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.r BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.i BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.z BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.u-p.g BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.g-p.r BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.r-p.i BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.i-p.z BETWEEN # AND #)  and (p.u-p.r BETWEEN # AND #)
